t Recharge','Rewards','Limited Time Event','Challenger Arena Week 2','Challenger Arena Week 4','Challenger Arena Sunday','Let\'s head back to the city. I\'ll tell you the details in due time.','Make sure to accept tasks as they offer great rewards.','Head back to the city to continue the task.','Our squad needs more members. Let\'s travel to the <color=#a23cf0>Headhunter</color> and take a look!','Once you\'ve finished the task, remember to head back to the city and claim your reward!','You can earn plenty of gold each day through <color=#a23cf0>Patronage</color>.','Remember to tap <color=#a23cf0>Save Lineup</color>.','Now that we can use <color=#a23cf0>Exploration</color>, we\'ll gain access to even more resources.','The <color=#a23cf0>Brawl Dungeon</color> has been unlocked. Test your mettle against other players and earn a variety of rewards.','Let\'s take a look at our idle resources.','Resources earned from training will be sent here. Don\'t forget to collect them.','There\'s strength in numbers. Join a <color=#a23cf0>Guild</color> to work together with like-minded individuals.','You can join an existing guild or create your very own.','Now that <color=#a23cf0>Daily Tasks</color> are available, we\'ve got another way to fill our coffers each day. Don\'t forget about them!','Login Rewards have been enabled. Let\'s go take a look.','Now we\'ll be able to claim <color=#a23cf0>Daily First Recharge</color> rewards. Let\'s check them out.','The <color=#a23cf0>Rewards Pool</color> has been unlocked. Let\'s go take a look.','From the <color=#a23cf0>Rewards Pool</color>, we can <color=#a23cf0>check in every day</color> to earn rare rewards!','Now we\'ll be able to engage in <color=#a23cf0>material collection</color>.','As the name suggests, <color=#a23cf0>material collection</color> can provide us with a large amount of materials and other rewards. Let\'s give it a shot.','Time for a new journey.','Now that the <color=#a23cf0>Battle of Corruption</color> is unlocked, le